  "extra_note_tr": "İngilizce gelecek zaman nüansları: 1. Will → ani karar, tahmin, vaat (It will rain. I'll help you!). 2. Be going to → niyet, plan, kanıt (Look at the clouds! It's going to rain. I'm going to study tonight). 3. Present Continuous → kesinleşmiş plan, randevu (I'm meeting her at 5 pm tomorrow). Zaman ifadeleri: tomorrow, next week, soon, in the future, tonight vb. 'Will' kısaltması: I'll, you'll, he'll, she'll, it'll, we'll, they'll. Olumsuz: won't, isn't/aren't going to."
